rong>This proves the failure of this government's tactics</strong>:<br />\n<br />\nForce the protesters to act violently and hope the public opinion will turn against the protesters.<br />\n<br />\nSo the large number of people came out to protest on 18 August is a win of a major battle because we have defeated a large scale offense conducted by the government. But I want to give this warning:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">U.S.A. won almost all major battles, but she lose the War of Vietnam.</span><br />\n<br />\nNow, enjoy our victory of this battle, and then we should work hard to win the war.<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Remember this: we need to win many battles before we win the war.</div></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"fbb91916b00ffe8bed81f2eaf0d585e26e2e1d3f","tid":1486873,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T09:44:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"58903f7778e4d09afcf66ada7d8b8569ecab6391","tid":1486873,"uid":88123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T09:47:46.000Z","msg":"我淨係知fb個個掛住J個光環，明明大把緊要嘢"},{"pid":"04ea24ddf824b01b0ccf5e72e90c0d344e125857","tid":1486873,"uid":30251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T09:50:23.000Z","msg":"暴力係手段而唔係目的，所有暴力行為係為咗比壓力政府而不是想破壞社會。<br />\n出師要有名先可以成功"},{"pid":"8f3029971628dc79d6686598786c0ac4af4a8a9c","tid":1486873,"uid":181035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T09:52:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d7943ea05843c8cfb652c96b22d79eeb5a3d529c","tid":1486873,"uid":152225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T09:53:43.000Z","msg":"如果818 政府都唔回應。要直視之後點做！"},{"pid":"436df5949e3f312bd92fb3e75d95c2ed294540f2","tid":1486873,"uid":247798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T09:56:00.000Z","msg":"不分和勇"},{"pid":"57a8416a4c03d8e5838eb582a4d77de6edfaea71","tid":1486873,"ui